{"tid":229167,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"杜汶澤公開撐陳冠希       FB引用「20字經文」","createTime":"2017-05-04T12:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T09:05:16.000Z","uid":58099,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"54654be91e6d602d33b52c3e226f84dd7a386054","tid":229167,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:03:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/m28335201705046_pmi63.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fm28335201705046_pmi63.png&h=a7089953&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳冠希事件再成為全城熱話，不過今次唔關閃卡事，而係陳冠希在機場被記者激嬲發惡一事，再次成為焦點，唔同嘅係，今次人人撐Edison。就連一向敢言的杜汶澤都幫口。<br />\n<br />\nEdison在官方Facebook只上載了自己接受訪問的相，很禮貌地沒有放記者的照片，沒帶任何文字。而杜汶澤今早在Facebook發帖，內容只有短短幾百字，引用聖經經文撐陳冠希「你們中間誰是沒有罪的 ，誰就可以先拿石頭打她 。」暗示香港人不應再因幾年前的閃卡事件批判陳冠希。<br />\n<br />\n雖然杜汶澤稱自己不是基督徒，但被網友大讚帖文中肯，經文Quoto得好，無論係閃卡定生BB都是陳冠希都私隱，大家不要迫得太緊等食花生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/m28335201705046_pmi63.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fm28335201705046_pmi63.png&h=a7089953&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b2a32c20e883097d80f20cdb0519b070c16d608","tid":229167,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:03:39.000Z","msg":"垃圾杜汶澤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0fd098c97721ccd71c7d33e931d7232a648e56e","tid":229167,"uid":41394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:17:42.000Z","msg":"50步笑100步 好地地做下傻強咪算囉"},{"pid":"a2b537a0e3055e714dc644204943b45153131938","tid":229167,"uid":78900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:22:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾杜汶澤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你條兔唇狗雜種仲垃圾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你老母當初係咪同野豬扑野扑左你件人間低賤物種出黎<img src=\"/assets/f